UK Prime Minister Boris Johnson will pay a two-day visit to India, beginning on April 21, according to the Prime Minister's Office. Johnson will first visit Ahmedabad, the largest city in Gujarat on April 21, and then travel to New Delhi to meet Indian Prime Minister Narendra Modi on April 22. (Cover: Prime Minister Boris Johnson delivers a speech at Lydd Airport in Dover, UK, April 14, 2022. /CFP)